<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٦٠٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">اللَّهُ عَنْهُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أَنّ النَّبِيَّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> رَأَى رَجُلًا يَسُوقُ بَدَنَةً،<span class="c5"> فَقَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(ارْكَبْهَا)</span>.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(ارْكَبْهَا)</span>.<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> إِنَّهَا بَدَنَةٌ،<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">(ارْكَبْهَا)</span>. ثَلَاثًا.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٢٦٠٣، ٥٨٠٧]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
